[Sensors]
   │  MQTT publish (JSON)
   ▼
[ Mosquitto Broker ]
   │  topics: greenhouse_<gh>/area_<a>/sensor_<id>/measure
   ▼
[ deviceConnector ]
   │  validates → enriches → forwards
   ▼
[ Catalog API (CherryPy) ] ──> [ PostgreSQL DB ]
        │                           │
        │                           └─ tables: users, sensors, measurements, alerts
        │
        ├──> [ WebApp UI (Nginx/Vite) ]  charts, tables, login
        ├──> [ Telegram Bot ]  /start /help /status /subscribe
        ├──> [ ThingSpeak Adaptor ]  optional external telemetry
        └──> [ DataAnalysis ]
                 │ computes baseline/forecast
                 ├─> [ HumidityManagement ]
                 ├─> [ LightManagement ]
                 ├─> [ NutrientManagement ]
                 └─> [ TimeShift ]
                      ↑
                  control/# (MQTT) for actions/commands
